there are three model definition in the zip file.
the difference is:
model3.py use flat1 as the input of the fully connect layer
model2.py use flat2 as the input of the fully connect layer
both model2 and model3 works with toco.

i update the models.zip file. 
there are three model definition in the zip file.
the difference is:

both model2 and model3 works with toco.
